channel.title: How to open more than 1 acc
channel.description:
Im not sure if this is the right forum, or if this has been posted before, but here it is.
Step 1, log on to your first account.
Step 2, look in C:\WINDOWS\.jagex_cache_32 for uid
Step 3, cut and paste it into a different folder
Step 4, login with different account.
if this worked for you, plz reply back.
